longBusinessSummary: International Dispensing Corporation designs, manufactures, and sells proprietary packaging and dispensing solutions for the flowable food, beverage, medical, pharmaceutical, and chemical industries. The company's products include The Answer, a low-acid and aseptic tap that can dispense liquid foods and beverages continuously without refrigeration; and IDC/Cryovac SpeedFlex BIB filler, an ultra-high-speed filler for bag-in-box (BIB) products. The company offers its products in China, Korea, Mexico, Pakistan, India, Dubai, Saudi Arabia, Israel, Germany, and Italy. International Dispensing Corporation was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in New York, New York.
